            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>beef arayes</strong> to a baking tray and top with another baking tray</p>\r\n<p>Add a heavy weight (e.g an oven-proof dish) and put the trays in the oven for 15-18 min or until the <strong>beef</strong> is cooked through&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Tip: the heavy weight flattens the arayes to help them stay together</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
